<refsect1 id="libpigment-3-desc"><title>&desc-tt;</title>
<para>
<!--
&cmd; is a library for creating rich application user interfaces. It is used by
<citerefentry><refentrytitle>elisa</refentrytitle> <manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>.
-->
</para>
<para>
Pigment is a library for creating rich application user interfaces. It allows
for the embedding of multimedia contents such as audio and video via GStreamer.
Pigment uses a plugin system to support different rendering API such as OpenGL,
OpenGL ES, or Direct3D.
&cmd;.</para>
</refsect1>
